title: Tensorflow Error At Start of Training
body:
THIS IS NOT TECH SUPPORT FOR NEWBIE FAKERS
POST ONLY ISSUES RELATED TO BUGS OR CODE

## Expected behavior

I expected not to see any Tensorflow errors at the start of training.

## Steps to reproduce

I wrote my own bash script which performs all the necessary steps.  

Here is the training command in my script:

DeepFaceLab/main.py train --training-data-src-dir $workspace_dir/data_src/aligned --training-data-dst-dir $workspace_dir/data_dst/aligned --pretraining-data-dir pretrain --model-
dir workspace/model --model SAEHD

## Other relevant information

Python 3.8 via Anaconda
Ubuntu Linux 18.04
I cloned the latest repo as of 04/14/2021
I used the requirements-cuda.txt to pip install the python dependencies
